OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 08 JUL
OL,4,CBROADCAST STUDIOS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2021FHM The Queen visits the set of
OL,7,FCoronation Street. A red carpet is laid
OL,8,Fon the cobbles. Producer Iain MacLeod
OL,9,Fintroduces members of the cast,
OL,10,Fincluding William Roache, Barbara Knox,
OL,11,FSue Nicholls and Helen Worth outside
OL,12,Fthe Rovers Return. The Queen's previous
OL,13,Fvisit to the programme was in 1982.
